HOTAI MOTOR CO said unconsolidated sales
in February rose 15.69% to NT$6,550,143,000 from NT$5,661,859,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  2/2012           2/2011
Sales           6,550,143        5,661,859   
YOY%              15.69%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           15,580,968       18,835,343  
YOY%             -17.28% 
=================================================================
 